For FBR,Its found in Najena last level,the last of the 3doors,U must defeat
the subbosses of Najena in the previous 2 doors to obtain final key into
Najena's Room[yes,the baddy is same anme as place].Defeat her and u get the
FBR.However its for a group of level30+ I think.
